{"id": "1260684468147064912", "channel_id": "1260684468147064912", "type": 0, "author_id": "1137328302135181312", "author_name": "cra0261_", "author_bot": false, "content": "加錯標籤了，加成了第五期的，所以點網址投稿了\n\n命輪密契的選擇主要是以穩定和輕鬆為主，然後在輕鬆的前提下盡快殺王\n本身有在養精通密契，而且對應命輪也有3啟的都可以試一下\n\npdf的截圖放在了下面\n另外，如果是用手機看的話，下面也放了個大字版pdf，只是排版可能比較差，因為我只是單純全選然後調了字號", "timestamp": "2024-07-10T19:49:59.591000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-06T09:52:23.621000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 17}], "attachments": [{"id": "1260684468293992539", "filename": "24s.pdf", "content_type": "application/pdf", "size": 628956, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1260684468147064912/1260684468293992539/24s.pdf?ex=69faf2a7&is=69f9a127&hm=8e0fbabf12dbc54caa81f0c0b7b242d123731858b0bffca1da500aaf406f9b3e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1260684468147064912", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "命定24詳細指南，手把手帶你克服癲5恐懼症", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1260606022977060904", "channel_id": "1260606022977060904", "type": 0, "author_id": "1223503015852380160", "author_name": "squire5771", "author_bot": false, "content": "本来我是只打350摆烂的，看到这期过375的人数挺多的也跟着打了一遍，感觉难度确实不大。\n按从后往前的顺序打的，第五波宁妃强度最高，我用了我最熟练的御四家，融灾环境混沌钥能狂气转不动，只好卖死抗一波命定秒了。这期甚至没有用到24，大家参考的时候可以24替换萝坦。\n第四波父母队无脑过，希洛莉莉补一点伤害。\n第三波灵摆眼，深海队随便乱打。\n第二波的大树有出血，会复活召唤小怪，尤乌队比较好打。借了个羊妈来帮助尤乌，苟住发育就行，第一条命用沸腾吧血戳死然后下回合开大直接秒群。\n第一波用深海盾击，灵摆给的卡可以拿三张艾尔瓦打击和30%最大生命护盾，艾尔瓦可以清怪给的废卡防止卡手，开静海龟缩慢慢磨就行。\n五波一共触发五次死亡抵抗，目前是所有375里面触发死抗最少的，参考价值肯定是够的。", "timestamp": "2024-07-10T14:38:16.805000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-10T15:05:08.238000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1260606023463473302", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-10-22-02-59-807_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 234894, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1260606022977060904/1260606023463473302/Screenshot_2024-07-10-22-02-59-807_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb5258&is=69fa00d8&hm=4fa2f25d5e382942b6912216ec918baa309e81a5cc88fc9eed63dce557504230&"}, {"id": "1260606023950139553", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-10-22-02-08-298_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 309857, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1260606022977060904/1260606023950139553/Screenshot_2024-07-10-22-02-08-298_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb5259&is=69fa00d9&hm=f47d481256922a6f967c0ed3d66aa5affe134c75eb91e84dcc75b3b64a5a95ae&"}, {"id": "1260606024461717504", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-10-22-02-20-854_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 323481, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1260606022977060904/1260606024461717504/Screenshot_2024-07-10-22-02-20-854_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb5259&is=69fa00d9&hm=fc2db69a2922eb2519d2ef5223e24a7f222f795140742806ee2bfbb133acfb6b&"}, {"id": "1260606025027817472", "filename": "Screenshot